    RegularizerR1ToR1
    public class RegularizerR1ContinuousToR1Continuous
extends NormedR1ContinuousToR1Continuous
implements RegularizerR1ToR1
    RegularizerR1ContinuousToR1Continuous computes the Structural Loss and Risk for the specified Normed R1 Continuous To Normed R1 Continuous Learning Function.

    • Alon, N., S. Ben-David, N. Cesa Bianchi, and D. Haussler (1997): Scale-sensitive Dimensions, Uniform Convergence, and Learnability Journal of Association of Computational Machinery 44 (4) 615-631

    • Vapnik, V. N. (1998): Statistical learning Theory Wiley New York
